title: Awarded Dana/FENS funding
date: 2022-12-20
inline: false
---
I am very happy to announce that Sara Calzolari and me obtained funding from <a href="https://www.dana.org/">Dana</a> and <a href="https://www.fens.org/">FENS</a> for our Brain Awareness project. Our proposed project will engage the general public of Birmingham with various activities at a the <a href="https://macbirmingham.co.uk/">Midlands Art Centre</a>. I look forward to organizing this event, togehter with my colleagues at the Centre for Human Brain Health. 
